==== Shift the records down ====
* First convert to S-Records using [https://github.com/douggilliland/Retro-Computers/tree/master/PC%20Tools/srecord srec_cat]
<pre>
srec_cat monitor.hex -Intel -o shifted.s -Motorola
</pre>
* S-Record output
<pre>
S123800000000800000080084DF80C0042AE004A422E0048422E00496136610005D861009A
S1238020044E49FA09D06164207C0000C00020100C80524F4D3266044EA800084E714E71EB
</pre>
* Then shift and save as HEX file
<pre>
srec_cat shifted.s -offset - -minimum-addr shifted.s -o monshifted.hex -Intel
</pre>
